title: EP 44: '90s Head Ft. BBOD, Maino, and Uncle Murda
itunes:title: EP 44: '90s Head Ft. BBOD, Maino, and Uncle Murda
description:
Love and Hip Hop’s BBOD gave some Lip Service to Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire about the definition of friendship, tips to stay fresh, using a washcloth instead of a tampon, and passionate connections in the studio. Then Maino and Uncle Murda crash the interview and talk about being judged from their past, masturbation, and Maino clears his name.
